title: Dialogos from the depths to the heights w/ Jonathan Pageau and Paul Vanderklay- Voices with Vervaeke
description:
Paul, Jonathan, and I have a wonderful dialogos about emergence and emanation, dialectic and narrative, symbolism and reality. Really wonderful and joyful.
